It's a little confusing to figure out the roleplay on pets.<P>On the one hand, it's an element from another plane; earth, air, etc. As someone said, you can send it back to the plane whenever. Don't get attached.<P>Yet on the other hand, the pet has a name. It talks with you. I read somewhere they're considered sentient. They save the party at times and you can get attached.<P>But I too have adopted the "they're elements you summon; you command them" line. Use them as you need.<P>--------------------<P>Arch Mage 60<BR>Master of the elemental epic magics<BR>Collector of Robes
